code: @Override public Boolean apply(Object left, Object right) {     if (this != NULLEQ && (left == null || right == null)) {         return null.     }     return doApply(left, right). }
@Override public final Boolean doApply(Object left, Object right) {     return process.apply(left, right). }

@Override public Object process(Object input) {     if (function() == BinaryComparisonOperation.NULLEQ) {         return doProcess(left().process(input), right().process(input)).     }     return super.process(input). }
